Introduction
============

libpib is a userspace driver for Pseudo InfiniBand HCA.
It is a plug-in module for libibverbs that allows programs to use
Mellanox hardware directly from userspace.  See the libibverbs package
for more information.

Using libpib
==============

libpib will be loaded and used automatically by programs linked with
libibverbs.  The pib kernel module must be loaded for HCA devices
to be detected and used.

Supported OS
==================

libpib supports the following Linux:

    CentOS 6.x 

